        "\n",
        "First, visualise the two principal eigenvectors $\\textbf{e}_{1,2}$ together with an input vector $\\textbf{h}_{i}$ by plotting the element values as a function of node index $k$ (e.g., using the function `matplotlib.pyplot.step()`.  \n",
