        "\n",
        "$$\n",
        "\\textbf{v}_{i+1} = \\textbf{v}^\\mathit{eq}_i + \\left(\\textbf{v}_i - \\textbf{v}^\\mathit{eq}_i \\right) \\, \\exp( -\\Delta t )\n",
